name: Figma Covers
description:
Use these presets as Figma file covers in your projects or Figma Community files. New presets are added regularly, so you can vary from project to project. The included guides help you that nothing of your precious cover will get cut off!


Features

  • Easy to customize
  • Guide explaining he anatomy
  • Supports Figma files and Figma Community
  • New presets added regularly
